---
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-32 border-b border-subtle relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FDFBF7] z-0"></div> <!-- Subtle warm background -->

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 text-[#9B2226]">
        <span class="lang-ar">المنهجية: من الملاحظة إلى النظام</span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Methodology: From Observation to System</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <span class="lang-ar">
          لتجنب القرارات المبنية على الذوق الشخصي، تم اتباع منهجية منظمة.
        </span>
        <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">
          To avoid subjective design decisions, the project followed a structured methodology.
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Visual Diagram Flow -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 relative">
      <!-- Decor line connecting steps on Desktop -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-[40px] rtl:right-12 ltr:left-12 rtl:left-12 ltr:right-12 h-1 bg-[#9B2226]/10 z-0 rounded-full"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-subtle shadow-sm relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#9B2226]/20 mb-4 font-mono">01</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">
          <span class="lang-ar">الملاحظة</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Observation</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">
          <span class="lang-ar">تم تحليل ٨٩٢ مراجعة من جوجل.</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">892 Google reviews were examined.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-subtle shadow-sm relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#9B2226]/20 mb-4 font-mono">02</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">
          <span class="lang-ar">اكتشاف الأنماط</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Pattern Identification</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">
          <span class="lang-ar">تم تحديد المواضيع المتكررة كجودة الطعام وتجربة الضيافة.</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Recurring themes such as food quality, social gatherings, and hospitality atmosphere were identified.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-subtle shadow-sm relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#9B2226]/20 mb-4 font-mono">03</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">
          <span class="lang-ar">التحقق البحثي</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Research Validation</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">
          <span class="lang-ar">تمت مقارنة النتائج مع دراسات تجربة المستخدم والضيافة.</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Patterns were compared with established UX and hospitality research.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#9B2226]/30 shadow-md relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#9B2226]/40 mb-4 font-mono">04</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-[#9B2226]">
          <span class="lang-ar">بناء النظام</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">System Design</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-secondary">
          <span class="lang-ar">تم تحويل النتائج إلى أنظمة تصميم واضحة (ألوان، خطوط، تصوير، بنية).</span>
          <span class="lang-en hidden" dir="ltr">Insights were translated into design systems covering typography, color, photography, motion, and layout.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
